and then particularly in four,

00:02:06.408 --> 00:02:08.209
I don't recall seeing anything

00:02:09.223 --> 00:02:13.968
this a greatly specific to what we are

00:02:13.989 --> 00:02:16.731
experiencing and what we're offering as

00:02:16.831 --> 00:02:22.557
