going to try to find uh where we

00:06:40.685 --> 00:06:42.307
uh where I think I have found it

00:06:42.346 --> 00:06:45.290
to where we were previously so rejoining

00:06:45.550 --> 00:06:48.232
our efforts in the the greatest song ever

00:06:48.252 --> 00:06:50.495
sung it is devoted entirely to dote his

00:06:50.514 --> 00:06:51.795
name has been mentioned already

00:06:52.196 --> 00:06:52.815
Twice in it,

00:06:52.875 --> 00:06:55.776
no one else's name is presented in it.

00:06:56.697 --> 00:06:59.737
We are now in a position to commence

00:07:00.458 --> 00:07:02.439
with it now that we know that Dowd

00:07:02.559 --> 00:07:04.959
is the person that Yahowah has declared

00:07:05.379 --> 00:07:08.920
that he would and now has enabled the

00:07:08.939 --> 00:07:10.961
benefits of his covenant through Dowd.

00:07:11.420 --> 00:07:13.221
and that Dowd is the chosen one,

00:07:13.322 --> 00:07:19.403
that Dowd is the person that Yahowah has

00:07:19.863 --> 00:07:22.964
elected to work through to accomplish all

00:07:22.985 --> 00:07:23.564
