00:07:33.728 --> 00:07:34.747
based on these statements,

00:07:34.767 --> 00:07:36.189
there can be no Jesus Christ,

00:07:36.209 --> 00:07:38.249
and there can be no Bar Kokhba.

00:07:38.850 --> 00:07:39.490
This is

00:07:41.065 --> 00:07:44.428
emphatic that Dowd is the one.

00:07:45.228 --> 00:07:47.670
So as we rejoin,

00:07:47.711 --> 00:07:49.952
we find that one after the next,

00:07:50.012 --> 00:07:53.654
every word of this declaration contains a

00:07:53.814 --> 00:07:55.817
treasure trove of relevant insights.

00:07:56.476 --> 00:07:57.937
The same is true with these next

00:07:57.958 --> 00:07:58.459
statements.

00:07:58.519 --> 00:08:00.579
They are awesome individually and

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:02.321
exceptional collectively.

00:08:02.882 --> 00:08:05.463
Dowd's status with God is both

00:08:05.923 --> 00:08:09.406
extraordinarily special and absolutely

00:08:09.687 --> 00:08:10.127
secure.

00:08:11.778 --> 00:08:12.218
It reads,

00:08:12.278 --> 00:08:15.180
he himself will call out to me and

00:08:15.221 --> 00:08:17.023
he will welcome me announcing,

00:08:18.043 --> 00:08:23.007
you are my father.

00:08:25.649 --> 00:08:30.353
I also will appoint and make him my

00:08:33.216 --> 00:08:33.817
firstborn.

00:08:35.418 --> 00:08:36.458
My firstborn son.

00:08:37.961 --> 00:08:39.261
The Elyown.

00:08:41.597 --> 00:08:44.078
highest and most uppermost,

00:08:45.179 --> 00:08:56.366
the very influence of God in comparison to

00:08:57.307 --> 00:08:58.868
kings and rulers of the earth.

00:09:00.509 --> 00:09:02.750
I'm sorry that I appeared to get

00:09:02.789 --> 00:09:03.791
distracted there.

00:09:04.071 --> 00:09:04.912
I just was

00:09:06.706 --> 00:09:08.346
staggered by the implications.

00:09:08.947 --> 00:09:10.967
I know what is written here.

00:09:11.067 --> 00:09:14.690
I've translated this, commented on it,

00:09:16.130 --> 00:09:17.951
provided insights regarding it,

00:09:18.111 --> 00:09:22.274
and shared it at least on four occasions

00:09:22.333 --> 00:09:23.734
as part of the Yahowah blog,

00:09:24.095 --> 00:09:25.174
the Eighty-Ninth Mizmowr.

00:09:25.715 --> 00:09:27.716
And it's presented, I think,

00:09:28.035 --> 00:09:30.457
four or five times throughout these books.

00:09:30.477 --> 00:09:33.698
So there is a very special place that

00:09:33.759 --> 00:09:35.460
it holds in our hearts.

00:09:36.969 --> 00:09:41.912
overall uh understanding of god who he is

00:09:41.971 --> 00:09:43.993
what he's offering and through whom he

00:09:44.033 --> 00:09:50.096
works so this is still extraordinary and

00:09:50.115 --> 00:09:51.856
the reason it's so extraordinary to me is

00:09:51.876 --> 00:09:56.499
that two and a half billion people today

00:09:57.278 --> 00:10:00.461
and billions prior to them have been

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:01.981
beguiled into believing

00:10:02.864 --> 00:10:07.246
That a person now known as Jesus Christ

00:10:07.947 --> 00:10:08.527
was real.

00:10:09.488 --> 00:10:13.230
That God became a man.

00:10:14.711 --> 00:10:16.672
That men could kill God.

00:10:17.812 --> 00:10:19.854
And that bodily resurrection was somehow

00:10:20.533 --> 00:10:21.875
possible and beneficial.

00:10:23.635 --> 00:10:26.977
And that Jews were the ones who killed

00:10:26.998 --> 00:10:27.118
them.

00:10:29.841 --> 00:10:33.684
It boggles the mind because none of it's

00:10:33.725 --> 00:10:34.065
true.

00:10:34.085 --> 00:10:38.909
And the fact is that God has said

00:10:39.910 --> 00:10:43.274
emphatically here in the eighty ninth

00:10:43.494 --> 00:10:47.857
psalm already that David is the Messiah.

00:10:48.498 --> 00:10:50.860
There is no reference to a Jesus being

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:52.020
a Messiah anywhere.

00:10:52.782 --> 00:10:54.264
Says David is the Messiah.

00:10:55.214 --> 00:10:57.375
And if that were not enough,

00:10:57.736 --> 00:11:01.179
it goes on to say that now here

00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:03.923
that it's Dowd who is the son of

00:11:03.962 --> 00:11:08.888
God and that Yahowah is his father.

00:11:08.947 --> 00:11:12.230
But it doesn't even end there.

00:11:13.072 --> 00:11:16.235
Christians would claim that Jesus was

00:11:16.335 --> 00:11:16.836
fully God.

00:11:18.913 --> 00:11:20.475
And yet, while that's impossible,

00:11:21.095 --> 00:11:24.616
God is not and will never be a

00:11:24.657 --> 00:11:25.017
man.

00:11:26.077 --> 00:11:28.918
All of God won't fit into this universe

00:11:29.139 --> 00:11:32.721
of two or more trillion galaxies.

00:11:32.801 --> 00:11:34.822
It won't fit into one galaxy.

00:11:34.841 --> 00:11:36.582
It won't fit into one solar system.

00:11:36.602 --> 00:11:37.864
It won't fit into one planet.

00:11:38.344 --> 00:11:39.804
It most certainly won't fit into one

00:11:39.884 --> 00:11:41.666
hemisphere or one nation,

00:11:42.066 --> 00:11:43.427
much less one person.

00:11:43.447 --> 00:11:46.268
And

00:11:47.628 --> 00:11:49.408
Here, God explains that.

00:11:51.090 --> 00:11:52.610
Not only is Dowd the Messiah,

00:11:52.910 --> 00:11:54.792
not only is Dowd the one through whom

00:11:54.831 --> 00:11:56.472
Yahowah worked his ebed,

00:11:57.134 --> 00:12:00.375
not only is Dowd the chosen one,

00:12:00.416 --> 00:12:02.697
and not only is Dowd the man through

00:12:02.756 --> 00:12:04.398
whom the covenant was enabled,

00:12:05.418 --> 00:12:07.139
which means the one through whom salvation

00:12:07.179 --> 00:12:10.101
was provided and access to God was given.

00:12:12.322 --> 00:12:13.403
But on top of all of that,

00:12:14.744 --> 00:12:17.326
Dowd is Elyown.

00:12:19.740 --> 00:12:22.341
Elyown is as powerful a term as there

00:12:22.402 --> 00:12:23.482
is in the universe.

00:12:25.182 --> 00:12:29.625
Elyown means that Dowd is the very essence

00:12:29.705 --> 00:12:30.926
of God's influence.

00:12:34.027 --> 00:12:35.047
El means God.

00:12:36.488 --> 00:12:40.870
The Yod speaks of the hand of God,

00:12:41.169 --> 00:12:43.291
the influence of God.

00:12:44.370 --> 00:12:47.393
And the On means all things pertaining to

00:12:47.452 --> 00:12:47.732
this.

00:12:48.634 --> 00:12:52.096
So Elyown means all things pertaining to

00:12:52.136 --> 00:12:53.376
the influence of God,

00:12:54.258 --> 00:12:57.500
which means that while Dowd is not God,

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:03.182
Dowd is going to return and become the

00:13:03.201 --> 00:13:07.924
very influence of God in our presence.

00:13:07.985 --> 00:13:11.706
He's the very substance of God's hand.

00:13:12.407 --> 00:13:15.408
Whatever God wishes to accomplish,

00:13:16.442 --> 00:13:18.302
throughout all eternity,

00:13:19.244 --> 00:13:22.806
is going to be done through dote.

00:13:23.326 --> 00:13:27.107
That's what Elyown means.

00:13:27.187 --> 00:13:29.210
And so rather than saying something

00:13:29.350 --> 00:13:31.711
stupid, like Christianity,

00:13:32.091 --> 00:13:37.114
where this mythical figure known as Jesus

00:13:37.154 --> 00:13:40.636
Christ becomes the fullness of the

00:13:40.677 --> 00:13:45.519
Godhead, making Jesus a God, which is...

00:13:47.024 --> 00:13:49.126
Not only pagan, but utterly absurd,

00:13:49.246 --> 00:13:49.866
impossible.

00:13:51.729 --> 00:13:53.690
God is very astute.

00:13:54.230 --> 00:13:59.714
And he says that his son, Dowd,

00:13:59.734 --> 00:14:02.274
is going to become the very influence,

00:14:02.316 --> 00:14:06.677
the very hand of God in our presence.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:11.782
So let me just...

00:14:12.903 --> 00:14:15.205
Read through that one more time because

00:14:15.225 --> 00:14:17.784
you need to process this.

00:14:19.225 --> 00:14:22.106
He himself, this is Dowd,

00:14:23.826 --> 00:14:26.048
will call out to me and welcome me

00:14:26.207 --> 00:14:29.368
announcing, Hugh Karahani.

00:14:30.068 --> 00:14:34.029
Qara, I just wish, oh, excuse me.

00:14:34.509 --> 00:14:37.571
Qara's my little, my wife's little puppy.

00:14:37.971 --> 00:14:39.850
And she just ran to on top of

00:14:39.910 --> 00:14:42.251
my feet with me calling out her name.

00:14:44.024 --> 00:14:46.044
Well, Qara was named after Qara.

00:14:46.725 --> 00:14:52.107
Qara is the actionable root of Miqrah.

00:14:52.868 --> 00:14:56.389
Miqrah adds my to Qara to tell us

00:14:56.429 --> 00:15:00.410
to ponder all things pursuant to Qara

00:15:01.211 --> 00:15:03.111
being invited and summoned,

00:15:03.732 --> 00:15:05.874
being encouraged to read and recite,

00:15:06.413 --> 00:15:10.855
being welcomed such that we engage in a

00:15:10.995 --> 00:15:11.336
meeting.

00:15:12.267 --> 00:15:15.587
while being called out and announcing.

00:15:16.347 --> 00:15:20.528
So Qara is the essence of the Miqraey.

00:15:20.629 --> 00:15:23.210
The Miqraey are the very essence of the

00:15:23.269 --> 00:15:24.350
path to God.

00:15:24.830 --> 00:15:27.750
And it is Dowd who fulfilled the first

00:15:27.791 --> 00:15:31.412
three, the spring Miqraey, Pesach, Matzah,

00:15:31.692 --> 00:15:32.511
and Bikuwrym.

00:15:33.032 --> 00:15:35.633
So here he himself will call out to

00:15:35.692 --> 00:15:38.052
me and welcome me, announcing,

00:15:38.513 --> 00:15:40.994
issuing this invitation to meet.

00:15:42.491 --> 00:15:46.734
such that we should read and recite all

00:15:46.813 --> 00:15:49.416
